Package magellan.client.swing.tree

Class SimpleNodeWrapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • magellan.client.swing.tree.DefaultNodeWrapper
      • magellan.client.swing.tree.SimpleNodeWrapper
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CellObject, Changeable, SupportsClipboard, SupportsEmphasizing
    public class SimpleNodeWrapper
extends DefaultNodeWrapper
implements SupportsClipboard, Changeable
    A SimpleNodeWrapper wraps some object, displays a text and a set of icons and has a clipboard value.
